				<h2>Is the input of ESC really limited at 50 Hz and will the PID controllers work properly?</h2>
<p>Based on the wiki page of ESC, the ESC generally accepts a nominal 50 Hz PWM servo input signal whose pulse width varies from 1 ms to 2 ms</p>

<p><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Electronic_speed_control" rel="nofollow">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Electronic_speed_control</a></p>

